title: Combat Flight Simulator 3_Updates and data files only!
description:
This is a compilation of PUBLIC DOMAIN software. CFS3 IS NOT INCLUDED HERE!! Updates and data files ONLY!!!It is available free on the internet. The files here are for Combat Flight Simulator 3!. The add-ons have already been inserted into the program. Includes all updates from Microsoft, Nationality expansion set, No CD crack, Plus the data files from a copy of CFS3 with over 150 aircraft and dozens of missions. Scenery and weapons add-ons too numerous to list.Visit unclestinkstradingpost to see updates & add-ons for other simulator programs.
                         Be kind to others.
                            PLEASE SEED!!!
